{
  "stem": "21817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was really rough on me because I didn't understand a lot of things and I had to guess.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But somehow I managed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from November till, till '41, I was in school leading to normal life to a certain degree but I was missing my mother and my sisters.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father was-- it was terrible with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He could not-- he could not take it, I mean, that he left his wife and children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at one point, he wanted to go back to, to Mlawa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a registration in Bialystok that whoever wants to register can register and go back and bring the families.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was a trick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father did not register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had somebody else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he had a-- one of his friends over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had registered himself to go back to Poland to bring his family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, they encircled the whole city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had the list of every, every person who wants to go back to, to Germany or Poland and the rest of them and they took them away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian army or the [NON-ENGLISH], or the secret police, or whatever they call it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They arrested those people at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put them in a big, big cattle trains The-- and they all wind up in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they said, if you want to go back to Germany, you are a spy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the policy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But fortunately enough for me, my father did not register because he had-- he had a feeling or he knew something which he didn't tell me, that he cannot do it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in 1940, he, he got contact with my mother and sisters.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
